hich the essential norm is $\\geq C$ and for which\n$\\lambda I+D$ is not a compact perturbation of a coercive operator for any real\nor complex $\\lambda$ with $|\\lambda|\\leq C$. Finally, we resolve negatively a\nrelated open question in the convergence theory for collocation methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 May 2021 16:21:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Nov 2021 10:09:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-05"}
