igure\nup to 10 protection routings for RCube DCNs. As far as we know, in past\nresearch, there were at most three protection routings developed in other\nnetwork structures. Finally, we summarize some crucial analysis viewpoints\nabout the transmission efficiency of DCNs with heterogeneous edge-core servers\nfrom the simulation results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 May 2021 18:34:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-09"}
