 conclusion in Ref. [3] with GR theory that the ultra-compact objects from\nnegative branch of semi-classical gravity with a linear equation of state are\nunable to generate demanding gravitational echoes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 May 2021 06:18:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-21"}
